value.description:
Pyroclastic rock in which greater than 25 percent of particles are greater than 64 millimeter in
			largest dimension. Includes agglomerate, pyroclastic breccia of Gillespie and Styles (1999). Schmid 1981;
			LeMaitre et al. 2002.

